                                             <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                                                <p>His journey started in the 1980s, from a small village in India and stepping into Bollywood to become an Actor. From a young age, he was drawn to the world of acting and always dreamed of playing negative roles (Villain) in movies. With an unyielding dedication to his craft, he wanted to make his dreams a reality. But for that, he needed to get into the industry. He started off in 1981 with a Movie ‘Naseeb’ where he worked as an Exhibitor, the film was a big hit because of its Grand Star cast. He kept on working as an Exhibitor for some time and was a part of many big Movies like Kranti, Silsila, and Nikah.</p>
